      "id": "section-3",
      "number": "3.",
      "heading": "Preemption.",
      "text": "A home rule\nunit may not fix the compensation of elected officers of that unit of local\ngovernment in a manner inconsistent with this Act. This Act is a limitation\nunder subsection (i) of Section 6 of Article VII of the Illinois Constitution\non the concurrent exercise by home rule units of powers and functions exercised\nby the State.",
      "history": "",
      "source_url": ""
    },
